{"tid":2211933,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"珉娥28歲生日快樂！　經紀公司更新近況⋯點開照片有洋蔥","createTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T09:47:58.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"55ef1ff02c26c9b7603b9cf9500c1a4a9f0eda85","tid":2211933,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:09:57.000Z","msg":"南韓女團AOA前成員珉娥在7月時，自爆在團體內遭到成員霸凌、父親過世時被關在衣櫃等，還在Instagram上傳怵目驚心的割腕照，讓大批粉絲相當擔心，所幸她目前乖乖接受心理治療，生活漸漸回歸正軌，21日正值她的28歲生日，經紀公司上傳了多張照片，引起大批網友討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5155/d5155184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5155%2Fd5155184.jpg&h=d4edfc5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5061/d5061146.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5061%2Fd5061146.jpg&h=24410a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲珉娥目前正接受心理治療，慢慢恢復生活。（圖／翻攝珉娥IG）<br />\n<br />\n珉娥在自爆遭AOA隊友霸凌且曾多次試圖自殺後，為了專注於心理治療，將Instagram關閉，21日正值她28歲的生日，經紀公司「Woori Actors」也替她更新了近況，貼出一系列照片寫下「真的非常感謝，這麼疼愛（珉娥），這些禮物我們會好好轉交給她的」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5155/d5155186.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5155%2Fd5155186.jpg&h=96c8fb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5155/d5155185.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5155%2Fd5155185.jpg&h=1847fcc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲珉娥在21日度過生日，粉絲紛紛寄禮物到公司給她。（圖／翻攝Woori Actors IG）<br />\n<br />\n然而，在「Woori Actors」上傳的照片中，可以看出有許多歌迷製作了禮物，要一起慶祝珉娥的28歲生日，其中一張特別製作的蛋糕上，有翻糖製作的珉娥人偶，旁邊寫下「不管什麼時候，永遠在這裡陪伴妳」，短短一行生日訊息就讓許多網友紅了眼眶，紛紛留言表示「希望珉娥接下來的日子都可以好好的」、「珉娥生日快樂，一定要幸福喔！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5155/d5155187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5155%2Fd5155187.jpg&h=5a62fbbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲粉絲製作生日蛋糕，旁邊給珉娥的訊息藏洋蔥。（圖／翻攝Woori Actors IG）<br />\n<br />\n欺凌妹正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1725c0f49d6d0ca9a0f0fc0c7d5068f5b0fd6b","tid":2211933,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T12:27:36.000Z","msg":"佢憔悴左好多 希望佢快啲好返 提起精神"},{"pid":"bc3a4420b066a39d931bc2ff2f44b2c9ee040ce9","tid":2211933,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-22T09:47:58.000Z","msg":"斯凌妹做乜唔入嚟講幾句"}]}